                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4198" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0054</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9497 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场机制VS政府干预：H省旅游客运交通管理体制改革之争</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Market Mechanism VS Government Intervention: Controversy over the Reform of Tourism Transportation Management System in H Province </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">童碧莎，王学峰，陈怡宁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">H省旅游客运管理服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">旅游客运交通；市场机制；政府干预；旅游市场秩序；零负团费</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">tourism transportation; market mechanism; government intervention; tourism market order; below-cost tour fee</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例介绍了2005年以来，H省在旅游业发展过程中，为解决长期以来“零负团费”导致的旅游客运交通市场秩序紊乱问题而不懈进行的三次旅游客运交通管理体制改革历程。在这三次改革过程中，H省主要运用政府干预的手段，先后经历了“政府牵头，企业主导”的省统一旅游汽车服务中心阶段（2005~2009）、“政府主导、财政拨款”的省旅游客运管理服务有限公司阶段（2009~2014）、“政府主导，行业自律”的省旅游客运服务中心阶段（2014~2018）。三次改革均不同程度招致了来自各方的争议。争议的核心集中于“市场之手”与“政府之手”之争：市场经济环境下到底是应该顺应市场规律充分发挥市场的自发调节机制，还是继续以政府为主导，发挥政府干预作用？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case introduces three times of reform of tourism transportation management system in H province since 2005 which aimed in solving the disorder of tourism transportation market caused by below-cost tour fee for a long time. During the three reforms, H Province mainly used the means of government intervention, and has experienced three stages. The first stage is called the provincial unified tourism vehicle service center stage (2005-2009) which is characterized by &quot; enterprise self-management with governmental supporting &quot;. The second stage is called provincial tourism transportation management service limited company stage (2009-2014) which is characterized by &quot;government leading with governmental financial support&quot;. The third stage is called provincial tourism transportation service center stage (2014-2018) which is characterized by &quot; industry self-regulation with governmental leading &quot;. The three reforms have aroused controversy from all sides. The core of the controversy focuses between &quot;market hand&quot; and &quot;government hand&quot;: should we follow the market rules and give full play to the spontaneous regulation mechanism of the market, or should we continue to insist in the government leading model and play the full role of government intervention in the market economy?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游经济学》、《旅游政策与法规》等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场失灵的原因；政府干预的必要性；政府干预的手段；政府干预失灵的原因和表现</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
